{"tid":2329581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警8.31推跌孕婦 途人理論反涉阻差辦公被捕 區議員斥賊喊捉賊","createTime":"2020-12-17T10:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T10:59:53.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1088b04236a1ae8beb11ed591a916c851f4a48","tid":2329581,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"大批市民今年8月31日到太子站聚集紀念去年8.31事件，警方當晚掃蕩期間，在旺角亞皆老街推倒一名孕婦，孕婦的丈夫當時亦被拘捕。事隔近4個月，當區區議員林兆彬指，事件中有途人周三（16日）被警察上門拘捕，涉嫌阻差辦公，暫准保釋。林指當日是警員推倒孕婦引起事端，批評警方濫捕，賊喊捉賊。警方回應則指，當晚在拘捕一名男子時，另一名女子「懷疑以手推開警員」，阻礙行動，經進一步調查後昨作出拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n余認為，馮先生及太太在事件上均為受害者，途人見到有需要的人而挺身協助，「俠義相助」反而遭到拘捕，實屬「冇天理」。他指，警方突然作出拘捕，或反映警方掌握新資料，女途人的處境可能比馮先生更不利，但不能排除馮先生一同被控告的機會。他估計，另一位途人、以至馮太太都有可能同樣被拘捕，將與律師團隊繼續跟進事件。"},{"pid":"0ca87b896ba8fb7aee7361b1d32f24c6f39d898f","tid":2329581,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/VNVA5JOLOVDARIGXWEY6BAOLUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FVNVA5JOLOVDARIGXWEY6BAOLUM%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28XwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=171e9e15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FVNVA5JOLOVDARIGXWEY6BAOLUM%2F&h=15c471d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/VNVA5JOLOVDARIGXWEY6BAOLUM/</a>"},{"pid":"9106391cee17fe01bf195c7c6b9fd72017301d06","tid":2329581,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45aec3c8e9419ef9340ca3dd639d9a8b61b540d","tid":2329581,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"